  "text": "We have set up the discussion of lower-dimensional string theories without referring explicitly to their ten-dimensional origins since we believe they deserve study in their own right, and exhibit physics that are very particular to their precise form (a simple example being the dimension of space-time). However, it is often helpful to realize their roots in ten dimensions. They arise from NS5-branes or singularities inside a Calabi-Yau manifold, in a double scaling limit [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] in which the string coupling is taken to zero while keeping ",
